{"tid":285477,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大陸新一代] 貴州高校門外水浸　清潔工揹學生離校惹議","createTime":"2017-06-15T23:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T06:45:39.000Z","uid":25125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38c0d94e23e863468e2ca412c67abe828c30c6fa","tid":285477,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T23:34:01.000Z","msg":"貴州高校門外水浸　清潔工揹學生離校惹議<br />\n06月16日(五) 04:29<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170616/photo/bkncn-20170616042903756-0616_05011_001_01b.jpg?20170616044819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170616%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170616042903756-0616_05011_001_01b.jpg%3F20170616044819&h=d86e6468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貴州多地連日來遭遇大暴雨侵襲，六盤水師範學院教學樓門口前日大量積水，校方遂請清潔女工幫忙搭建通道，其中更有工人揹着學生離校，引發網民爭議，認為大學生不應中年的清潔阿姨揹。事後有學生澄清，由於當時水比較深，阿姨穿着水靴，不忍心學生涉水才揹他們，也有很多男生揹女生。<br />\n<br />\n從現場片段可見，由於道路嚴重水浸，水深及膝，大批學生站在校門外的樓梯，未能離開。校方於是清潔女工利用長櫈搭成通道，好讓學生回家。其中多名女工更揹着女生離校，隨即引起網民爭議。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民批評：「可笑至極！鞋濕了會死嗎？」、「怎麼忍心讓年紀那麼大的阿姨揹過去」，又直言：「即使是女生，也沒有那麼嬌貴，如果是我不會讓阿姨揹，阿姨也是人啊，沒有義務揹」。惟亦有人持相反意思，稱：「只要人家是自願揹的，這有甚麼關係？不能因為他是環衞工，你就覺得可憐」。<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170616/bkncn-20170616042903756-0616_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170616%2Fbkncn-20170616042903756-0616_05011_001.html&d=rXNzXHNz84wjncQk%2Ft7N%2B8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=94d394cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170616/bkncn-20170616042903756-0616_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n咁多人年紀輕輕對腳就跛左<br />\n真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c191f9b7e954bb9202cf56313e3e45ed080d333","tid":285477,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T23:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad720fbfb3f5cdc37ed231affa8127f3cda3d3f","tid":285477,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T23:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee272d39526a9543b3a42dfbc659b04f7afc0ecb","tid":285477,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:21:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地都好意思喎"},{"pid":"365db6a1806cdf016a7a0c44b2867283180708fe","tid":285477,"uid":30487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:27:03.000Z","msg":"所以話中國未來打仗輸撚硬<br />\n成班少爺兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accbddf151dd16b46c6a5504985feaf79cdd5ed8","tid":285477,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:27:44.000Z","msg":"香港有班柒頭成日宣揚大陸仔好刻苦捱得<br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6fa725a2276b16eb8c658890dd54100e54fc18","tid":285477,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:28:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以話中國未來打仗輸撚硬<br />\n成班少爺兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一孩政策下個個都係少爺小姐"},{"pid":"2163c0e4cacb2117c6d39af237a9c45e6346585f","tid":285477,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港有班柒頭成日宣揚大陸仔好刻苦捱得<br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪以前唔想係大陸捱<br />\n所以仆街都要黎香港生活個班呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55021313f35a8a51f6d5d28400f41110f67da49","tid":285477,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"